  "text": "The studies described above suggest that flow experience is a significant cognitive state in online virtual community behavior that may influence serious gameplay and learning. In the future, online environments (and the functions and tasks they present to users) will need to facilitate flow experience. Hence, it is imperative that designers of virtual worlds understand the mechanisms underlying the enjoyment of virtual experiences and flow. This is argued by [CITATION_1] , who called for further research into flow because of its important contribution to our understanding of the optimal experience.",
